entry.title: What Python means in Namibia
entry.summary:
Description

I will be looking at the importance of python in our country, how does it change our lives . I will introduce myself to outside world as a python programmer in Namibia, and whats the secret behind my posters during PYCON Namibia and how do I make it work. I will be looking at different (activities, projects) that we carry out as a PyNam Society and etc.
